{"type":"answer","id":253530,"parentType":"question","parentId":24196,"uid":9304,"contents":"1949年解放军攻太原城，其时三大战役已定国共胜负，阎锡山被蒋召跟去台湾。<br>\n阎锡山堂妹阎惠卿率军死守太原三月，最后城破自殉，留下《阎惠卿致阎锡山绝命电》一文。<br>\n电文文字壮烈气势恢弘。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EWuuW0nXkAICieJ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EWuuW0nXkAICieJ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EWuuW0nXkAICieJ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-04-30","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}